sequenceDiagram
    participant C as 呼叫端模組<br/>(BC/CP/BS/TL)
    participant S as 中央 DP Server<br/>SRVLB001
    participant D as SRVDP010<br/>標籤印表機查詢
    participant DB as 中央 DB
    participant L as LBSB01<br/>Listener :9200
    participant Q as Local Queue<br/>(local.db)
    participant P as GoDEX 印表機<br/>:9100

    C->>+S: Call SRVLB001<br/>bar_type, site_id, data_1~19<br/>(不傳 printer_id)

    S->>S: 1. 取得 Client IP

    S->>+D: 2. Call SRVDP010<br/>(client_ip, bar_type)
    D->>DB: 查 DP_COMPDEVICE_LABEL<br/>WHERE CLIENT_IP AND BAR_TYPE

    alt 找不到對應
        D-->>S: found=false
        S-->>C: {success: false,<br/>message: "資訊設備標籤要先設定"}
    end

    D-->>-S: found=true, printer_id=PRN-002

    S->>S: 3. 產生 UUID
    S->>DB: 4. INSERT LB_PRINT_LOG
    S->>DB: 5. SELECT LB_PRINTER<br/>WHERE PRINTER_ID='PRN-002'
    DB-->>S: SERVER_IP = 192.168.1.10

    S->>+L: 6. POST http://{SERVER_IP}:9200/api/lb/task<br/>Authorization: Bearer token<br/>Body: {uuid, printer_id, bar_type, data...}
    L->>Q: 寫入 LB_PRINT_LOG_CACHE
    L->>Q: INSERT ONLINE_QUEUE (status=0)
    L->>L: 放 1 個通知進佇列
    L-->>-S: 7a. 200 OK {success: true, uuid}
    S-->>-C: {success: true, uuid,<br/>printer_id: "PRN-002"}

    Note over Q,P: LBSB01 使用者操作列印

    Q->>P: EZPL 列印指令 (TCP:9100)
    P-->>Q: 列印完成
    Q->>Q: Status 0→1 (終態)<br/>RESULT: v1.1r1W80H35L40T0D8
